 - enemies
 - player goes through rooms avoiding enemies
 - to win player beats a # of rooms and defeats boss at the end
 - player progresses by clearing all enemies in the room
 - player defeats enemy with weapon
 - player starts with a weapon and finds different types of weapons throughout the rooms, this is a collectible item
 - different weapons do different damage
 - if an enemy touches a player, they lose a life
 - player starts with 5 lives
 - enemies chase the player
 - enemies get more difficult as the player goes through rooms
 - player can obtain a choice of power-ups after beating a room